    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## To Understand What We Type In the Code Node \"Convert To Json Output\" (Optional)\n\n- Make sure to setup both workflows properly\n- Run the workflow once first from the main workflow \n- Go into executions here \n- Open up a previous exection and click \"copy to editor\" to get the data \n- Pin the data from the \"when execute by another workflow\" node \n- Replace the \"Convert to Json Output\" with either of the code nodes below and run it once \n- You can now see what consists of \"aiResponse\" and \"rootData\" in the main code node",
